00:26:59.901 --> 00:27:03.467
Um, basically, every time
you ask the ad server for an ad,

00:27:03.467 --> 00:27:05.467
that's an ad request.

00:27:05.467 --> 00:27:07.467
Um, some percentage
of that time,

00:27:07.467 --> 00:27:10.868
we will return you
an actual ad to show.

00:27:10.868 --> 00:27:12.601
