00:27:12.601 --> 00:27:14.767
And you basically
take that percentage--

00:27:14.767 --> 00:27:16.400
that's your fill rate.

00:27:16.400 --> 00:27:19.801
Um, of the impressions
that you serve, um,

00:27:19.801 --> 00:27:22.701
people will either click
or they won't click on them.

00:27:22.701 --> 00:27:26.000
We measure that as your clicks
over your impressions,

00:27:26.000 --> 00:27:27.934
or your clickthrough rate.

00:27:27.934 --> 00:27:30.801
And then, uh, based
on your clickthrough rate,

00:27:30.801 --> 00:27:32.467
you have your revenue,

00:27:32.467 --> 00:27:34.901
so if you have, you know,
1,000 requests

00:27:34.901 --> 00:27:37.501
and let's say you get
1,000 impressions back,

00:27:37.501 --> 00:27:41.267
uh, you have, um, you know,
50 clicks on that,

00:27:41.267 --> 00:27:43.567
and say you're getting paid
5 cents a click,

00:27:43.567 --> 00:27:45.868
you're gonna get paid
accordingly that way.

00:27:45.868 --> 00:27:49.067
