00:27:52.100 --> 00:27:55.667
Uh, what that means is effective
cost-per-thousand impressions,

00:27:55.667 --> 00:27:57.801
so what it means is, uh,

00:27:57.801 --> 00:27:59.801
depending on what the--

00:27:59.801 --> 00:28:01.868
what the cost per click is

00:28:01.868 --> 00:28:04.868
for a particular ad, um,
you're--

00:28:04.868 --> 00:28:07.868
the amount of money you make
based on 1,000 impressions

00:28:07.868 --> 00:28:11.167
is going to fluctuate,
so we call that an eCPM,

00:28:11.167 --> 00:28:14.167
and that's basically the average
for 1,000 impressions

00:28:14.167 --> 00:28:16.367
that you get
from a particular ad network.

00:28:16.367 --> 00:28:19.267
Um, as you guys probably, uh,
